ificant\nafter longer storage times of typically 100-150 seconds and we then observe a\nconstant decay rate due to residual-gas collisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 31 Mar 2018 07:28:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-03"}
