 spatial profiles very\nsimilar to those of the Peregrine solutions of different orders. We present\nexample of three-soliton collision, for which even the temporal behavior of the\nmaximal amplitude is very well approximated by the Peregrine solution of the\nsecond order.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Mar 2018 22:44:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 6 May 2018 12:09:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 31 May 2018 23:18:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-24"}
